@startuml sequence_responsive
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Responsive Layout Strategy (L2-036, L2-037, L2-038, L2-061)

participant "Viewport" as vp
participant "Tailwind CSS\nBreakpoints" as tw
participant "Storefront Layout\n(L2-036)" as store
participant "Admin Layout\n(L2-037)" as admin
participant "Teams Layout\n(L2-038)" as teams

== Mobile (<640px / sm) ==
vp -> tw: width: 375px
tw -> store: Hero stacks vertically\nProduct grid: 1 column\nHamburger menu visible (L2-061)\nFull-screen nav panel on tap
tw -> admin: Sidebar collapsed (icon-only)\nTables scroll horizontally
tw -> teams: Sidebar hidden\nSingle-panel view

== Tablet (≥640px / md breakpoint) ==
vp -> tw: width: 768px
tw -> store: Product grid: 2 columns (md:grid-cols-2)\nHero side-by-side layout
tw -> admin: Sidebar icon-only\nContent area wider
tw -> teams: Sidebar icon-only\nTwo-panel view

== Desktop (≥1024px / lg breakpoint) ==
vp -> tw: width: 1200px
tw -> store: Product grid: 3-4 columns\n(lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4)\nFull hero layout, desktop nav visible
tw -> admin: Full sidebar with labels\nTables full-width
tw -> teams: Full three-panel layout\nChat + sidebar + detail panel

@enduml
